Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{=38}===============================DIALOGUE============================
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.49,0:02:40.96,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,Dez anos atrás, no East Blue...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.86,0:02:48.68,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{there was a small village called Windmill\NVillage where people lived peacefully - CR}{people lived in peace\Nin a hamlet called Windmill Village. - Yibis}havia uma pequena aldeia chamada\NVila dos Moinhos, onde as pessoas viviam em paz.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.36,0:02:52.70,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{but not far from it was Mt. Colubo\Nwhere people seldom stepped foot. - CR}{Nearby was Mount Colubo,\Nwhere people seldom ventured. - Yibis}Não muito longe dali ficava o Monte Colubo,\Nonde ninguém ousava entrar.{LP/Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.72,0:03:00.76,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{Only the strong could survive there and\Nthe weak who entered were doomed to die. - CR}Lá, só os fortes sobreviviam.\NQuanto aos fracos, a morte era praticamente certa.{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.46,0:03:06.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What I'm saying is, grandpa... - CR}{Grandpa, all I'm saying is... - Yibis}Vovô, eu tô te dizendo...{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.20,0:03:08.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'll become the King of the Pirates... - CR}{I'll be the Pirate King. - Yibis}Eu vou ser o Rei dos Piratas...{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.47,0:03:10.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Cut the crap! - CR}{What do you know about the pirate king?! - Yibis}Que papo é esse de Rei dos Piratas?!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.74,0:03:12.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Let me... Let me go! - CR}M-Me solta!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.91,0:03:16.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{On top of eating the Devil\NFruit, you're talking nonsense! - CR}Primeiro come aquela fruta do diabo,\Ne agora fica falando besteira!{Yibis/Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.78,0:03:19.22,Main-207+,,0,0,8,,{Luffy! Both you and Ace have to become - CR}{Luffy, both you and Ace - Yibis}Luffy! Você e o Ace{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.22,0:03:22.05,Main-207+,,0,0,8,,{the strongest Marines! - CR}vão ser Marinheiros exemplares!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.05,0:03:24.10,Main-207+,,0,0,8,,Ai, ai, ai, droga!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.10,0:03:26.47,Main-207+,,0,0,8,,{My body is rubber but why is it painful?! - CR}{My body is rubber, but this hurts! - Yibis}{\q2}Por que dói se meu corpo é de borracha?!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.47,0:03:28.05,Main-207+,,0,0,8,,Me solta, vovô!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.83,0:03:32.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It was a mistake to leave\Nyou in the Windmill Village! - CR}Deixar você na Vila dos Moinhos foi um erro!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.12,0:03:34.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Of all things, you like pirates?! - CR}Logo {\i1}piratas{\i0}, tinha que ser?!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.76,0:03:39.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What's this place? - CR}Que lugar é esse?{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.80,0:03:46.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Stop it!! Whoever you are,\Ndo you wanna get killed?! - CR}{Stop it already! Pound on\Nmy door, and I pound on you! - Yibis}Para com isso! Reze suas preces, seja lá quem for!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.00,0:03:47.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sou eu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.22,0:03:52.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{G-Garp-san! - CR}S-Senhor Garp!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.19,0:04:06.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You're looking good. - CR}Parece estar bem.{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.72,0:04:11.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Give me a break! Please,\Nyou gotta have mercy on me! - CR}Isso não tem graça! Por favor,\Nvocê não pode fazer isso comigo!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.60,0:04:14.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Ace is 10 years old now! - CR}Aquele garoto, o Ace, já tem dez anos!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.14,0:04:17.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Oh yeah, already? How is he? - CR}Ah, já? Como ele está?{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.77,0:04:19.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não tem graça!{CR}{Don't laugh at our expense! - Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.92,0:04:23.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We can't handle him anymore!\NYou have to take him! - CR}A gente não aguenta mais!\NVocê tem que levá-lo de volta!{Yibis/Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.73,0:04:24.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Deixando isso de lado...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.85,0:04:26.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Não{\i0} deixe de lado!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.78,0:04:28.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You're annoying, kid! - CR}Fica quieto, moleque!{LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.68,0:04:30.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Look after him, too. - CR}Quero que cuide dele também.{Polly}
Comment: 0,0:04:30.88,0:04:32.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Huh?{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.38,0:04:34.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hey, Luffy, say "hi" to them. - CR}{Hey, Luffy, say "hi." - Yibis}Ei, Luffy. Diz oi.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.49,0:04:35.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Yo! - CR}{Hi. - Z}E aí?{LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.32,0:04:38.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Who is that kid? - CR}Quem é o moleque?{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.02,0:04:40.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He is my grandson. - CR}É meu neto.{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.66,0:04:41.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What? - CR}Quê...?{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.39,0:04:43.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– O quê?!\N– O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.66,0:04:45.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{One more?! - CR}Mais um?!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.28,0:04:49.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He's Garp's... I mean, Garp-san's grandson?! - CR}Ele é neto do Garp... quer dizer, do Senhor Garp?!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.84,0:04:51.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Não dá!\N– Não dá!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.04,0:04:53.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Alright then, Here's your choice. - CR}Muito bem! Aqui estão suas opções:{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.40,0:04:56.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Do you wanna spend all your\Nlife in prison or raise him? - CR}{rot for the rest of your life\Nin a cell or raise him. - Yibis}Apodrecer o resto da vida\Nnuma cela, ou criar esse moleque.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.51,0:05:00.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{There are many crimes you\Ncommitted that I've overlooked. - CR}{I've overlooked who-knows-\Nhow-many of your crimes. - Yibis}Eu já fiz vista grossa\Npra sabe-se lá quantos crimes seus.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.00,0:05:03.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Come on! - CR}– Isso é injusto!\N– Isso é injusto!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.85,0:05:06.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Bom, eu não quero ser presa, mas...{CR}{I don't wanna get arrested but... - Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.82,0:05:12.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Sometimes I think that maybe it's better\Nto be in prison than take care of Ace... - CR}{Sometimes, I think that maybe it's better\Nto be in prison than to take care of Ace. - Yibis}{...sometimes I wonder if prison\Nis a better alternative to raising Ace. - Z}Às vezes eu acho que a cadeia pode ser\Nmelhor do que cuidar do Ace.{LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.41,0:05:15.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{But you want us to look after your grandson, too? - CR}{We also need to look after your grandson? - Yibis}E agora vai empurrar\Nseu neto pra gente?{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.10,0:05:17.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I bet he's also a monster. - CR}Aposto que esse moleque também é um monstro.{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.70,0:05:19.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Crappy shack! - CR}{What a crappy shack! - Yibis}Que barraco mixuruca!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.21,0:05:21.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You wanna fight?! - CR}{I'll knock you silly! - Yibis}Vou te mandar pra semana que vem!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.38,0:05:23.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Not listening! - CR}{and ignored! - Yibis}Ele me ignorou!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.47,0:05:23.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}– Chefe!\N– Chefe!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.00,0:05:24.68,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Você está bem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.68,0:05:28.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What is it?! Ugh, spit! Gross! - CR}{What's this?! Ugh, spit! Gross! - Yibis}Que isso? Ugh! É cuspe! Que nojo!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.72,0:05:29.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Who did it?! - CR}Quem fez isso?!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.14,0:05:32.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, você!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.21,0:05:35.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Say "sorry"! It's gross! - CR}Pede desculpa! Que nojo!{Z/Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.08,0:05:36.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Ace! - CR}{Oh?! Ace! - Yibis}Hm? Ace!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.72,0:05:39.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Are you back, Ace? - CR}{Ah! Are you back, Ace? - Yibis}Ah! Voltou, Ace?!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.32,0:05:46.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hey, say "sorry"! - CR}Ei! Pede desculpa!{Z/Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.76,0:05:53.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Luffy, esse é o Ace.\NEle é três anos mais velho que você.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.62,0:05:56.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You're gonna live here with them from today. - CR}A partir de hoje, vocês vão morar juntos.{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.44,0:05:57.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– O quê?!\N– O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.81,0:05:58.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You can't just do that! - CR}{That ain't decided yet! - Yibis}Isso ainda não tá decidido!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.74,0:06:05.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sejam legais!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.71,0:06:06.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tá decidido {\i1}sim{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.81,0:06:08.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Any problem with that? - CR}{Got a problem? - Yibis}Tem algum problema?{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.33,0:06:12.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We'll take him! - CR}– Será um prazer!\N– Será um prazer!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.82,0:06:16.69,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}É sua vez de lavar a louça!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.14,0:06:16.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Can I have some more, pops! - CR}Mais!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.06,0:06:18.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Can I have some more, pops! - CR}Me dá mais, coroa!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.43,0:06:20.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm a woman! - CR}Fique sabendo que eu sou mulher!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.59,0:06:23.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você sabe onde está agora?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.87,0:06:24.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.50,0:06:25.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Então eu vou te contar.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.98,0:06:29.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{This is a den of the Dadan family,\Nmountain bandits that rule Mt. Colubo! - CR}Você está no covil da família Dadan,\Nos bandidos da montanha do Monte Colubo!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.84,0:06:33.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Bandidos da montanha? Eu odeio bandidos da montanha!{CR}{Mountain bandits? I hate those guys! - Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.24,0:06:40.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Shut up, you little shit! We're\Nannoyed by having a kid like you! - CR}{Shut it, you little brat! Getting saddled\Nwith a punk like you is nothing but trouble! - Yibis}Cala a boca, pirralho! Quem se incomoda\Nsomos nós por ter que aguentar um moleque como você!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.21,0:06:42.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If you don't wanna stay here, that's fine! - CR}Se não gosta daqui, ótimo!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.32,0:06:44.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Go away and die like a dog somewhere! - CR}Vaza e morre feito um cachorro!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.87,0:06:46.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Easy, easy, boss. - CR}Calma, chefe.{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.58,0:06:48.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu quero comer mais...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.12,0:06:52.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I wanna have that meat, too. - CR}Me dá um pouco dessa carne também.{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.72,0:07:03.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{These are all from a bison that Ace brought. - CR}Toda essa carne é de um bisão\Nque o Ace abateu pra gente.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.90,0:07:07.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He gave us a cut of the\Ntake so everybody can eat. - CR}Ele nos deu uma parte da caça\Npra todo mundo poder comer.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.14,0:07:09.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The mountain bandits' world is rough sailing. - CR}A vida de bandido da montanha é dura.{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.21,0:07:12.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You're gonna have to work\Npretty hard from tomorrow! - CR}A partir de amanhã,\Neu vou te fazer trabalhar até não aguentar!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.05,0:07:16.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Limpeza, lavanderia,\Npolir sapatos e armas,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.44,0:07:19.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,furto, roubo, fraude e {\i1}assassinato{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.82,0:07:24.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Remember, you can't tell\NGarp what we make you do! - CR}E lembre-se: nunca conte\Nao Garp o que a gente te obriga a fazer!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.76,0:07:29.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{One bowl of rice and one\Nglass of water for a day! - CR}Você ganha uma tigela de arroz\Ne um copo d'água por dia!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.46,0:07:31.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso é tudo que eu posso te garantir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.66,0:07:36.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You gotta get everything else by\Nyourself and grow up on your own. - CR}{You gotta get everything else\Non your own. Fend for yourself, brat! - Yibis}O resto você tem que conseguir sozinho\Ne se virar por conta própria.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.00,0:07:36.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tá!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.92,0:07:40.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{"Okay"?! Why don't you cry or something? - CR}"Tá"?! Só isso?! Nem vai chorar?!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.24,0:07:44.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm fine because grandpa\Nthrew me into a jungle once - CR}{This one time, Grandpa\Nthrew me into the jungle, - Yibis}Uma vez o vovô me jogou numa selva!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.05,0:07:48.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{and there was water to drink and frogs,\Nsnakes, and mushrooms to eat in the forest! - CR}{and there was water to drink and frogs,\Nsnakes, and mushrooms to eat in the forest! - Yibis}{\q2}Isso aqui é uma floresta, então tem bastante água pra beber\Ne sapos, cobras e cogumelos pra comer!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.51,0:07:52.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Plus, I'll become a pirate someday so... - CR}E além disso, eu vou ser pirata um dia...{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.95,0:07:55.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{...I must be strong like that! - CR}{so I gotta take care of myself! - Yibis}então eu {\i1}tenho{\i0} que me virar sozinho!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.62,0:07:57.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Chefe!\N– Você está bem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.23,0:07:58.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What're you doing?! - CR}O que você tá fazendo?!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.62,0:08:01.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Here we go! - CR}– Eia!\N– Eia!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.16,0:08:04.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Where is he going?! - CR}Pra onde ele tá indo?{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.16,0:08:05.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Here we go! - CR}– Eia!\N– Eia!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.91,0:08:08.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Where are you going?! - CR}Pra onde {\i1}você{\i0} tá indo?!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.20,0:08:10.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você disse "pirata"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.64,0:08:12.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He's not listening! - CR}{...and ignored! - Yibis}Ele me ignorou!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.50,0:08:13.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.88,0:08:22.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{See? He's too tough! That's why I didn't wanna take care of Garp's grandson! - CR}Tá vendo? Eu sabia que ia dar trabalho! Por isso\Neu não queria cuidar do neto do Garp!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.82,0:08:24.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Easy, easy, boss. - CR}Calma, che–{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.39,0:08:27.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.55,0:08:29.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Me espera!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.26,0:08:32.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.86,0:08:39.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Meu nome é Luffy! Eu não tô mais\Nbravo por você ter cuspido em mim!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.74,0:08:46.51,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Por que você tá rindo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.51,0:08:51.41,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{\t(3987,0,1,\c&HFEFEFE&\3c&HFEFEFE&\4c&HFEFEFE&)}{He only spilled some booze on me.\NIt's nothing worth getting mad over. - CR}Ele só derramou um pouco de bebida em mim.\NNão vale a pena ficar bravo por isso.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.41,0:08:55.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's nothing worth getting mad\Nover. Let's become friends! - CR}Não vale a pena ficar bravo\Npor isso! Vamos ser amigos!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.51,0:08:56.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você vai pra algum lugar?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.39,0:09:06.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É um beco sem saída!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.45,0:10:04.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei! O Ace voltou!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.00,0:10:05.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Food! - CR}{– He brought food!\N– He brought food! - Yibis}– Comida!\N– Comida!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.54,0:10:10.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Ace, did you come back alone? - CR}Ace, você tá sozinho?{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.23,0:10:13.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Where is Luffy? I thought\Nthat you were with him. - CR}Ei, cadê o Luffy?\NEu achei que ele tinha ido com você.{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.96,0:10:15.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I don't know. - CR}Sei lá.{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.90,0:10:19.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Get hold of yourself, boss! - CR}Se controla, chefe!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.50,0:10:20.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What did you say?! - CR}{S'you were sayin'?! - Yibis}O que você disse?!{Z/Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.70,0:10:24.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I said it's not good that we\Nlost him on the first day! - CR}{I said it's unacceptable that we\Nlost him on the first day! - Yibis}Tô dizendo que é muito ruim\Nter perdido ele no primeiro dia!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.14,0:10:27.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Who cares! If he dies, he dies! - CR}Me deixa em paz! Se morrer, morreu!{LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.65,0:10:33.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm already giving up on Ace, too! - CR}{Besides, I've already lost all hope for Ace. - Yibis}Eu já desisti do Ace também!{Z/LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.96,0:10:39.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I don't care if he dies or not.\NI'll just tell Garp it was an accident. - CR}{It's no skin off my back if he dies.\NI'll just tell Garp it was an accident. - Yibis}Mesmo se ele morrer por aí,\Né só falar pro Garp que foi um acidente.{LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.30,0:10:43.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's true that "the devil's\Nchildren have the devil's luck"! - CR}Como dizem: "Filho de demônio\Ntem sorte de demônio."{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.36,0:10:45.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He's the devil's son! - CR}Ele é cria do demônio!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.42,0:10:52.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If the Government finds out about this,\Nwhat do you think they'd do to us?! - CR}Se o governo descobrir que ele tá aqui,\No que acha que fariam com a gente?!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.71,0:10:54.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Easy, easy, boss. - CR}Calma, chefe.{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.50,0:10:58.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você tá bebendo demais!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.69,0:11:02.45,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,Uma semana depois...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.10,0:11:05.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Chefe! Chefe Dadan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.29,0:11:06.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Who is it? - CR}Quem– Hã?!{Yibis/Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.91,0:11:08.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Who is it? - CR}Quem é...? Hã?!{Yibis/Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.55,0:11:09.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You! - CR}É você!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.72,0:11:13.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O Luffy voltou!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.04,0:11:19.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You fool! - CR}{You're alive! - Yibis}Seu...!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.50,0:11:22.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You're alive! You...! - CR}{Why, you little...! - Yibis}Sobreviveu, seu mole–{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.87,0:11:24.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Easy, easy, boss. - CR}Calma, chefe.{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.53,0:11:26.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Onde {\i1}você{\i0} estava?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.82,0:11:30.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Easy, easy. Where were you \Nand what were you doing? - CR}Calma! Onde você tava\Ne o que tava fazendo?{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.64,0:11:34.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I've been chased by wolves\Nat the bottom of the valley. - CR}Lobos ficaram me perseguindo pelo desfiladeiro.{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.05,0:11:37.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What were you doing at\Nthe bottom of the valley? - CR}O que você tava fazendo no desfiladeiro?!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.48,0:11:43.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Anyway, it's nice that you're okay. - CR}Enfim, que bom que você tá bem.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.22,0:11:43.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Yeah. - CR}É, que bom.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.99,0:11:45.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's not okay! - CR}{It's not nice! - Yibis}Bom coisa nenhuma!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.05,0:11:48.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A praga voltou!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.93,0:11:53.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Why don't you go to bed tonight?\NYou gotta work from tomorrow! - CR}Vai dormir logo! Amanhã eu vou te\Nfazer trabalhar que nem um burro!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.89,0:11:54.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Já?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.84,0:12:04.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What's up? - CR}Bom dia!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.90,0:12:07.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Are you gonna go somewhere today, Ace? - CR}Pra onde você vai hoje, Ace?{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.78,0:12:11.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Take me with you! Let's become friends! - CR}Me leva junto! Vamos ser amigos!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.78,0:12:13.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Wait for me! - CR}Me espera!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.62,0:12:16.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Boss! He's going after Ace again! - CR}Chefe! Ele tá correndo atrás do Ace de novo!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.75,0:12:20.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hey! You gotta do chores around the house! - CR}{Hey! You got chores to do! - Yibis}Ei! Você tem tarefas pra fazer!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.88,0:12:25.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{No thank you! - CR}Nem pensar!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.07,0:12:27.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You little shit! You're out of control! - CR}{You little turd! ...and ignored! - Yibis}Você é incontrolável, seu pestinha!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.46,0:12:28.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Easy, easy, boss. - CR}Calma, che–{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.88,0:12:30.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Traz ele de volta agora!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.87,0:12:31.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sim, senhora.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.51,0:12:33.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.15,0:12:53.73,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{He kept going after Ace and losing him. - CR}Mesmo sempre perdendo o Ace de vista...{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.26,0:12:59.32,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{But it went on everyday. - CR}ele continuou perseguindo dia após dia.{Yibis/Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.32,0:13:00.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.24,0:13:10.87,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{1 month... - CR}Por um mês...{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.21,0:13:13.61,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{2 months... - CR}Por dois meses...{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.74,0:13:15.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000102&\3c&H000102&\4c&H000102&\t(20,954,1,\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&)}Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.46,0:13:16.61,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{No matter if it rained - CR}Não importava a chuva...{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.00,0:13:19.20,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{and was windy... - CR}Não importava o vento...{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.46,0:13:23.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.35,0:13:27.06,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{Luffy kept going after Ace desperately. - CR}Luffy era implacável na sua perseguição a Ace.{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.16,0:13:35.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.38,0:13:47.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ace! Ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.08,0:13:50.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I can't believe he's coming\Nthis far. He's so persistent. - CR}{I can't believe he made it this far.\NHe's so stubborn. - Yibis}Não acredito que ele me seguiu\Naté aqui. Ele é muito persistente.{LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.79,0:13:54.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah, droga!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.89,0:13:59.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Damn! I lost him again! Ace runs so fast! - CR}Droga! Perdi ele de novo! O Ace é muito rápido!{Yibis/Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.66,0:14:01.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Is it Ace?! - CR}É você, Ace?!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.17,0:14:15.01,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,{That's the beast of Mt.\NColubo! No one can beat it! - CR}{That's the beast of Mount Colubo! He's got no chance! - Yibis}Esse é o monstro do Monte Colubo!\NNinguém consegue derrotá-lo!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.58,0:14:20.15,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,{Why is he not running?! It's gonna eat him! - CR}Por que ele não foge?! Vai ser devorado!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.36,0:14:24.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I-I feel weak at the knees! - CR}M-Minhas pernas não se mexem!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.28,0:14:26.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That fool! - CR}Tsc! Aquele pirralho!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.72,0:15:34.54,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{Now, Luffy had been chasing Ace for 3\Nmonths with cuts and bruises all over... - CR}Após três meses de cortes,\Nhematomas e perseguição sem fim...{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.63,0:15:43.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's the end of the forest. - CR}É o limite da floresta.{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.39,0:15:52.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Wow! What is this place? - CR}{It stinks! What's with this place? - Yibis}Uau! Que lugar é esse?!{LP/Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.49,0:15:58.79,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{There is a place like this on the North side\Nof Mt. Colubo where the Dadan family lives. - CR}{North of the Dadan Family's\NMount Colubo lies a neglected place. - Yibis}Ao norte do Monte Colubo, onde a\Nfamília Dadan mora, fica um lugar abandonado.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.70,0:16:05.15,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{It is a smoky pile of discarded junk. - CR}Fumaça emana sem parar\Nde pilhas de lixo descartado.{Yibis/Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.15,0:16:08.62,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{Unwanted things ended up here. - CR}{The useless and unwanted accumulate here. - Yibis}Coisas indesejadas se acumulam aqui.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.52,0:16:15.10,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{And here live rogues who were\Nshunned from mainstream society. - CR}{The inhabitants are all outlaws\Nwho have been banished from the kingdom. - Yibis}Seus habitantes são fora-da-lei,\Nrejeitados pela sociedade.{Z/Polly/LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.10,0:16:18.00,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{Unsurprisingly, it's a lawless area. - CR}Naturalmente, a lei não tem poder aqui.{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.71,0:16:22.72,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{Crime and disease abound\Nsince there are no doctors. - CR}{Without so much as a doctor, the area\Nruns rampant with both crime and disease. - Yibis}Sem nem ao menos um médico,\Na área é tomada por crime e doença.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.72,0:16:26.83,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{This place is called Gray Terminal. - CR}Este é o Terminal Cinza.{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.83,0:16:28.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Treasure, treasure! - CR}{Treasure... Treasure... - Yibis}Vem cá, tesouro...{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.85,0:16:31.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Is there anything valuable here? - CR}{There ain't nothin' worth sellin' here. - Yibis}Não tem nada de valor por aqui?{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.94,0:16:35.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Here's something! - CR}{I found some pearls! - Yibis}Achei uma coisa!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.83,0:16:37.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Give it to me! - CR}É meu!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.05,0:16:38.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That's mine! - CR}Não, é meu!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.84,0:16:40.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Stop it! I found it! - CR}{You gotta be kiddin'! I found 'em! - Yibis}Larga! {\i1}Eu{\i0} que achei!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.71,0:16:43.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Don't touch it, you fools! - CR}{Don't touch 'em, you bastards! - Yibis}Tira a mão, seus abutres!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.00,0:16:45.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Let me cash it in for you! - CR}{I'm gonna take 'em to town an' sell 'em! - Yibis}Eu vou vender na cidade!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.73,0:16:46.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You can't have it! - CR}{You ain't gettin' 'em! - Yibis}Nem pensar!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.72,0:16:48.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Stop! - CR}{Wait! - Yibis}Volta aqui!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.35,0:16:58.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Desgraçado!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.33,0:16:59.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Give it to me! - CR}Larga!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.14,0:17:05.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You wouldn't have gotten hurt\Nif you'd just given it to me! - CR}{If you'd just handed 'em over,\NI wouldn't have needed to sock ya! - Yibis}Se tivesse entregado logo,\Nnão precisava ter apanhado!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.65,0:17:08.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Thank you very much! - CR}{Good job! - Yibis}Bom trabalho!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.67,0:17:10.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You asshole! - CR}{Why, you...! Are you kiddin' me?! - Yibis}Seu...! Tá de brincadeira?!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.46,0:17:15.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ladrão!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.31,0:17:22.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Outta my way, brat! - CR}Sai da frente, moleque!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.96,0:17:27.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hurry up! Or I'm gonna... - CR}Anda logo! Sai da frente ou eu vou...{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.52,0:17:29.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele foi por ali!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.49,0:17:37.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sabo! Sabo, você tá aí?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.28,0:17:42.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah, Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.59,0:17:44.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Desculpa o atraso.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.57,0:17:46.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tá atrasado mesmo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.49,0:17:49.48,Main-207+,,0,0,8,,{I've already done some work in the city. - CR}Eu já fiz um trabalho na cidade.{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.36,0:17:55.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Oh yeah? Well, I did, too. - CR}Ah, é? Na verdade, eu também.{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.20,0:17:57.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{At once! - CR}{– Here we go!\N– Here we go! - Yibis}– Ao mesmo tempo!\N– Ao mesmo tempo!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.00,0:18:00.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Whoa! You got a lot! Way more than I did! - CR}{Amazing! You got even more than me! - Yibis}Caramba! Isso é muito...! Muito mais do que eu consegui!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.63,0:18:03.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That's a lot of money! How'd you get that? - CR}{This is a lot of treasure! How'd you get it? - Yibis}Que butim! Como você conseguiu?!{Z/LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.81,0:18:07.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I robbed some thugs near the main gate! - CR}Roubei de uns bandidos perto do Portão Principal.{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.40,0:18:10.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Damn! You won again! - CR}{Damn! You beat me again today. - Yibis}Droga! Você ganhou de novo!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.67,0:18:12.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It doesn't matter if you win or lose. - CR}Não importa quem ganha, né?{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.01,0:18:16.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's been 5 years - CR}Esse fundo pirata é de nós dois.{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.62,0:18:19.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{since we started\Nto put money in our "pirate savings". - CR}Já faz cinco anos\Nque a gente começou a juntar, né?{Yibis/Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.71,0:18:23.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We worked hard for it. - CR}A gente se esforçou muito.{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.29,0:18:26.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Yes, we did. - CR}Com certeza!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.74,0:18:32.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We're gonna leave the East Blue and go\Nsomewhere these people have never dreamed of. - CR}{To leave the East Blue and into the world\Nthese island hicks couldn't even dream of... - Yibis}Deixar o East Blue e navegar por um mundo\Nque os caipiras dessa ilha nem conseguem imaginar...{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.50,0:18:35.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's exciting just to think about it! - CR}só de pensar eu já fico empolgado!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.32,0:18:45.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Now put it away. We can't\Nlet anybody to see it. - CR}Fecha logo a tampa.\NNunca se sabe quem pode estar olhando.{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.51,0:18:49.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I wonder how much we need\Nto get a pirate ship. - CR}{How much you think\Nwe'll need for a pirate ship? - Yibis}Quanto você acha que\Na gente precisa pra um navio pirata?{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.87,0:18:53.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I don't know. 10 million\Nor 100 million maybe? - CR}Quem sabe? Centenas de milhares,\Nou talvez milhões...{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.71,0:18:55.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Long way to go. - CR}Um dia a gente chega lá.{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.31,0:18:56.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,"Um navio pirata"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.39,0:19:01.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You guys! Are you gonna become pirates?! - CR}Vocês vão ser piratas?!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.36,0:19:03.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm gonna become one, too! - CR}{So am I! Me too! - Yibis}Eu também vou ser um!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.80,0:19:05.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.87,0:19:16.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Fica quieto!\N– Fica quieto!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.52,0:19:23.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Ace! I didn't know that you\Ntravel this far everyday! - CR}Ace! Então é pra cá que\Nvocê vem todo dia?!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.64,0:19:24.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Cala a boca.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.84,0:19:28.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Is this the Luffy that\Nyou were talking about? - CR}{So this is the pest...\Nthat Luffy guy you were talking about. - Yibis}Então esse é o tal Luffy que você me falou.{Z/LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.68,0:19:31.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah, você falou de mim?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.32,0:19:33.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I told him how annoying you are. - CR}{To complain about how clingy you are. - Yibis}Reclamei do quanto você é persistente.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.85,0:19:37.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He also told me that you're empty-headed. - CR}{And how you never think\Nabout what you're doing! - Yibis}E do quanto você parece não pensar em nada!{Z/LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.42,0:19:39.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Oh yeah? - CR}Entendi!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.42,0:19:42.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You don't realize that\Nwe're dissing you, do you? - CR}Ele nem percebe que a gente tá xingando ele?{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.67,0:19:45.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He finally got me here - CR}Ele finalmente me seguiu até aqui.{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.64,0:19:48.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{although I didn't take any walkable routes. - CR}{And I even made sure to avoid\Nthe paths most people use. - Yibis}E eu ainda evitei os caminhos principais.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.54,0:19:52.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Are you a friend of Ace's?\NBe my friend, too, buddy! - CR}{Hey, you! Are you Ace's friend?\NWe're friends too, right? - Yibis}Você é amigo do Ace?! Seja meu amigo também!{LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.88,0:19:56.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Shut up! You can't call me "buddy"! - CR}Cala a boca! A gente nem se conhece!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.55,0:19:58.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Então, qual é o seu nome?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.40,0:19:59.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sa–
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.20,0:20:00.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm not telling you! - CR}Não vou te contar!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.82,0:20:04.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É por isso que eu falei pra você morar aqui comigo!{CR}{This is why I said you should just live here! - Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.05,0:20:08.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The daily round trip--training on the\Nmountain road turned out to be bad! - CR}{It's a pain that your "training" means\Ndaily round trips through the mountains! - Yibis}Essa sua ideia de "treino" fazendo\Niadas e vindas pela montanha foi péssima!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.76,0:20:10.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What should we do? - CR}O que a gente faz?{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.40,0:20:13.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He found our secret. - CR}Agora ele sabe do nosso segredo.{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.64,0:20:16.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He's gonna tell somebody if nothing is done. - CR}{If we let him go, he'll blab to everyone. - Yibis}Ele vai abrir o bico se a gente não fizer nada.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.26,0:20:24.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A gente tem que matar ele.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.30,0:20:26.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Certo, vamos nessa.{CR}{Right. Good idea. - Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.20,0:20:27.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quê...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.21,0:20:30.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.09,0:20:36.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Don't kill me!! Help me!! I don't wanna die!! - CR}Não me mata! Me salva!\NEu não quero morrer!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.88,0:20:38.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Shut up, you fool! - CR}Seu idiota! Fica quieto!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.82,0:20:41.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Sabo, kill him already! - CR}Sabo! Anda, faz logo!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.29,0:20:43.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What?! You do it! - CR}{Why do I have to do it?! You do it! - Yibis}Por que eu?! Faz você!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.22,0:20:45.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu nunca matei ninguém!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.54,0:20:48.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Me, neither! And I don't know how! - CR}Eu também não! Eu não sei como faz!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.47,0:20:51.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Don't throw me into water! - CR}{Please don't drop me in the water! - Yibis}Por favor, não me joga na água!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.41,0:20:52.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Okay, let's head to the river! - CR}Certo! O rio!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.85,0:20:55.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Why did he tell us that? - CR}{Why'd he tell us? - Yibis}Por que ele contou?!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.30,0:20:56.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He's stupid! - CR}Porque ele é burro!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.33,0:20:58.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Help me!! - CR}Me salva!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.87,0:21:00.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Cala a boca!\N– Cala a boca!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.71,0:21:03.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I don't wanna die! - CR}Eu não quero morrer! Não!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.74,0:21:05.56,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,{I don't wanna die! - CR}Eu não quero morrer! Não!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.56,0:21:07.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I hear a voice from the forest! - CR}{I heard a voice from the forest! - Yibis}Tem uma voz vindo da floresta!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.68,0:21:08.81,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,É uma voz de criança!{CR}{It's a kid! - Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.81,0:21:11.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Oh no! Somebody's coming! - CR}Ah, não! Alguém tá vindo!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.12,0:21:13.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Set him free for now! - CR}Vamos desamarrar ele!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.48,0:21:16.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We gotta move from here\Nor they're gonna find our treasure! - CR}Se a gente não sair daqui, vão achar nosso tesouro!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.91,0:21:22.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Everybody knows those kids\Naround here. Ace and Sabo. - CR}Aqueles pirralhos, Ace e Sabo,\Nsão infames por aqui.{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.60,0:21:25.89,Main-207+,,0,0,8,,{Are you sure that it was - CR}Você tem certeza absoluta{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.89,0:21:28.35,Main-207+,,0,0,8,,{Ace who took the money? - CR}de que foi o Ace que roubou a grana?{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.35,0:21:32.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Yes. We're sorry. We shouldn't\Nlet our guard down. - CR}{Yeah, it's so embarrassing.\NWe let our guard down. - Yibis}É... É vergonhoso, mas a gente vacilou.{Z/LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.47,0:21:35.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{How outrageous that kid is! - CR}Não acredito naquele moleque...{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.08,0:21:38.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He can't just steal our money! - CR}metendo a mão na grana da nossa tripulação!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.66,0:21:43.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If Captain Bluejam finds out about\Nthis, he's gonna kill all of us! - CR}Se o Capitão Bluejam souber\Ndisso, a gente tá morto!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.32,0:21:50.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Dammit! I didn't know that those\Nthugs were working for Bluejam! - CR}Droga! Aqueles bandidos eram capangas do Bluejam?{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.09,0:21:53.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You mean that you stole the money from them? - CR}Bandidos? Quer dizer que você pegou\Naquela grana {\i1}daqueles{\i0} caras?{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.81,0:21:56.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I shouldn't have taken that money... - CR}A gente botou a mão\Nnuma grana perigosa...{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.64,0:22:00.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He has a real sword. That's\NPorchemy who works under Bluejam. - CR}{That guy carrying the sword is\NBluejam's underling, Porchemy. - Yibis}Ele tem uma espada de verdade...\NÉ o Porchemy, um dos capangas do Bluejam.{Z/LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.38,0:22:04.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He's crazy. Did you know that? - CR}{He's nuts. Have you heard? - Yibis}Ele é maluco. Você já ouviu?{Polly/Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.48,0:22:09.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He strips off your scalp alive\Nafter you lose a fight with him! - CR}Quando ele vence alguém, ele arranca o couro cabeludo vivo!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.54,0:22:16.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Let's just let them pass for now... - CR}{We gotta lay low. - Yibis}Tomara que eles passem direto...{LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.82,0:22:19.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Oh? Where is he? - CR}Hã? Cadê ele?{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.13,0:22:26.12,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{Let me go! What do you want from me? - CR}Me solta! O que vocês tão fazendo?{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.97,0:22:26.14,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,{How could you get caught? - CR}– Como ele foi pego?!\N– Como ele foi pego?!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.80,0:22:28.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Who is this little shit? - CR}{Who is this kid? - Yibis}Quem é esse pirralho?{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.45,0:22:29.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Help me! - CR}Me ajuda!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.64,0:22:31.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.82,0:22:34.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Me salva, Ace!{CR}{Please save me, Ace! - Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.63,0:22:39.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That fool! He's calling my name! - CR}{That idiot! He shouted my name! - Yibis}Seu idiota...!\NGritando meu nome assim...!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.63,0:22:39.00,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{ - CR}Ace! Ace! Ace!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.17,0:22:42.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Did you just call for "Ace"? - CR}Você disse "Ace"?{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.42,0:22:44.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{So what?! - CR}É, e daí?!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.19,0:22:47.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você conhece o Ace?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.86,0:22:50.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm his friend! - CR}Ele é meu amigo!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.11,0:22:53.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Oh, but he just tried to kill me. - CR}Ah, mas ele ia me matar agora mesmo.{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.36,0:22:58.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That fool! He's such a big mouth! - CR}Para. De. Falar.{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.82,0:23:00.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I don't know if you know about this but - CR}Preciso perguntar...{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.69,0:23:05.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I heard that Ace stole some\Nmoney from us and ran today. - CR}{Earlier today, Ace stole our money and ran off. - Yibis}Hoje cedo, o Ace roubou\Numas granas nossas e fugiu.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.97,0:23:09.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You don't know where is it now, do you? - CR}{You wouldn't happen to know\Nwhere he is, would you? - Yibis}Você por acaso sabe\Nonde ele guardou, sabe?{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.14,0:23:16.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Oh no! They're gonna take\Nall our treasure away! - CR}Ah, droga! Vão levar nosso tesouro!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.84,0:23:19.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I hope that fool doesn't tell them! - CR}{That airhead better not spill the beans! - Yibis}É melhor aquele cabeça oca não abrir o bico...{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.46,0:23:27.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– O quê?!\N– O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.26,0:23:28.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hã?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.65,0:23:31.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E-Eu não sei...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.56,0:23:34.17,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,{A terrible liar! - CR}Que mentiroso péssimo!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.36,0:23:42.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Alright, alright! It can't be\Nhelped that you don't know. - CR}Tá bom, tá bom. Se você\Nnão sabe, fazer o quê.{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.60,0:23:49.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Don't worry, I'll help you\Nbring back the memory! - CR}Eu vou te ajudar a refrescar a memória, relaxa!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.52,0:23:53.54,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{What are you doing?! Let me\Ngo! Where are you taking me?! - CR}Que isso?! Me solta!\NPra onde vocês tão me levando?!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.54,0:23:56.39,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{Dammit! Stupid! Let me go! - CR}Droga! Idiota! Me solta!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.39,0:23:57.42,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Seu desgraçado!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.15,0:23:59.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What should we do?! - CR}O que a gente faz?{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.67,0:24:02.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You know what we have to do... - CR}"O que a gente faz?" Bom...{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.74,0:24:12.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Me solta!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.60,0:24:14.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm not gonna tell you anything! - CR}Eu não vou falar nada!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.72,0:24:24.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Seu pirralho!{CR}{You damn brat! - Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.84,0:24:42.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I told you that my body turned to\Nrubber after I ate the Gum-Gum Fruit! - CR}{I tried to tell you, I'm rubbery\Nbecause I ate the Gum-Gum Fruit! - Yibis}Eu tentei te falar, mas eu sou de borracha\Nporque comi a Fruta Gomu Gomu!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.70,0:24:44.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Shut up! - CR}Quieto!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.51,0:24:47.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The Devil Fruit, eh? - CR}Uma fruta do diabo, hein?{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.08,0:24:51.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Looks like you had the real one. - CR}{Yeah, you're the real deal. - Yibis}É, parece ser genuíno.{Z/Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.62,0:24:55.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Get me a pair of gloves. - CR}Pega minhas luvas.{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.17,0:24:57.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Y-Yes, sir! - CR}Quê...?! S-Sim, senhor!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.15,0:25:01.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hurry up, hurry up! We're\Nscrewed if they come back! - CR}{Hurry! Hurry up! If Porchemy\Ncomes back, we're done for! - Yibis}Rápido! Rápido! Se o Porchemy\Ne os capangas voltarem, a gente tá ferrado!{Z/LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.35,0:25:04.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We gotta move our treasure somewhere else! - CR}{We gotta move the treasure fast! - Yibis}Temos que mover o tesouro rápido!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.56,0:25:08.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's a matter of time\Nbefore Luffy tells them! - CR}{It's only a matter of time\Nbefore that Luffy guy rats us out! - Yibis}É questão de tempo até\Naquele Luffy nos dedurar!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.32,0:25:11.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{They'll take not only what we stole from them - CR}{If they find this, they won't stop\Nwith what we stole from them, - Yibis}Se acharem isso, não vão levar\Nsó o que a gente roubou deles,{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.69,0:25:15.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{but all of our "pirate savings" that\Nwe've spent 5 years collecting! - CR}mas todo o fundo pirata\Ndos últimos cinco anos!{Yibis/Z/Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.35,0:25:23.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Escuta, pirralho.{CR}{Listen up, you brat! - Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.37,0:25:29.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The money that your friend Ace stole\Nis very important to our pirate crew. - CR}{The cash that your friend Ace stole\Nwas important to our pirate crew! - Yibis}A grana que seu amigo Ace roubou\Nera importante pra nossa tripulação pirata...{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.88,0:25:32.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{And you know where it is. - CR}e você sabe onde está!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.38,0:25:34.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{So I need you to tell us. - CR}{So... you will tell me. - Yibis}Então... você {\i1}vai{\i0} me contar.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.26,0:25:37.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{No! - CR}{Never! - Yibis}Não vou!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.79,0:25:46.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It worked! - CR}Essa doeu!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.93,0:25:53.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You don't wanna make a pirate mad! - CR}Você não devia irritar um pirata!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.90,0:25:59.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Our captain Bluejam is very brutal! - CR}{Our captain, Bluejam, is inhumanly brutal! - Yibis}Nosso capitão, Bluejam, é um monstro brutal!{Z/LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.56,0:26:09.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It hurts! I'm scared! - CR}Doeu! Tô com medo!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.11,0:26:10.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Help me!! - CR}Me salva!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.05,0:26:15.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Guys, go look for Ace and Sabo! - CR}Vocês, achem o Ace e o Sabo!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.92,0:26:18.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We don't have time to stand around! - CR}Não fiquem aí parados!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.52,0:26:19.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Sim, senhor!\N– Sim, senhor!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.95,0:26:31.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You're asking me if I know Ace and Sabo? - CR}{You want to know where Ace and Sabo are? - Yibis}Tão perguntando sobre o Ace e o Sabo?{Z/LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.01,0:26:33.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You guys must be hooligans from the city. - CR}{You guys are delinquents\Nfrom town, aren't you? - Yibis}Vocês devem ser delinquentes da cidade.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.80,0:26:37.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You don't wanna mess with those two. - CR}É melhor não se envolver\Ncom aqueles dois.{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.62,0:26:41.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{They're kids but you\Ncan't underestimate them. - CR}{They're kids, but don't underestimate 'em. - Yibis}Não subestime eles\Nsó porque são pequenos.{Z/LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.31,0:26:44.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{They're like mad dogs\Nthat'd kill even a tiger. - CR}{They're a pair of mad dogs\Nwho can even kill tigers! - Yibis}Aqueles dois cães loucos fazem picadinho de tigre!{LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.28,0:26:47.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Ace and Sabo? I haven't\Nseen them for a while. - CR}Ace e Sabo? Não vi eles...{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.24,0:26:50.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Anyway, young men, - CR}Mas mais importante, rapazes...{Yibis/LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.84,0:26:52.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{why don't you\Nleave everything valuable here? - CR}que tal entregar seus objetos de valor?{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.30,0:26:55.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{C-Come on, man! - CR}{P-Please don't! - Yibis}P-Prefiro não!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.49,0:26:57.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We'll ask someone else! - CR}Vamos procurar em outro lugar!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.63,0:27:02.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I didn't realize that it's almost night. - CR}{The sun's already setting. - Yibis}Já tá quase de noite...{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.30,0:27:05.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Yes! It's finished! - CR}{Alright, I'm done! - Yibis}Pronto! Terminei!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.31,0:27:07.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mudamos todo o tesouro!{CR}{I moved all the treasure! - Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.46,0:27:13.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.10,0:27:15.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sabo, o que foi?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.00,0:27:17.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Have they shown up to look for the money? - CR}{Did they try to loot our old hideout yet? - Yibis}Eles foram no nosso esconderijo antigo?{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.60,0:27:22.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{No, they haven't! - CR}Não, nunca apareceram.{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.24,0:27:24.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E aposto que não vão!{CR}{It's like they can't find it! - Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.01,0:27:25.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What do you mean? - CR}O que quer dizer...?{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.92,0:27:28.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That kid, Luffy... - CR}{That Luffy guy... - Yibis}Aquele Luffy...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.36,0:27:31.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He hasn't told them anything! - CR}ainda não contou nada pra eles!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.26,0:27:36.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm sure that they're torturing him! - CR}Com certeza estão torturando ele.{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.16,0:27:40.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I thought that he'd just tell them\Nbecause he's dumb and cries so much! - CR}{Since he's such a crybaby and an idiot,\NI thought he'd spill his guts right away! - Yibis}Ele era tão idiota e chorão que\Neu achei que ia contar na hora!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.41,0:27:41.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It doesn't make sense! - CR}Não faz sentido!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.77,0:27:45.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If nothing is done, he'll... - CR}Nesse ritmo, ele vai...{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.39,0:27:56.66,Main-207+,,0,0,8,,{It's so late! - CR}Tão atrasados...{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.22,0:27:59.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Who is in charge today? - CR}Quem era o responsável hoje?{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.59,0:28:03.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's Porchemy, Captain Bluejam. - CR}O Porchemy, Capitão Bluejam.{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.61,0:28:06.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's almost sunset. - CR}O sol já tá se pondo.{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.57,0:28:14.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm sure that they've already\Ncashed it in by now. - CR}Não tem como levar tanto tempo\Npra vender a mercadoria.{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.77,0:28:18.97,Main-207+,,0,0,8,,{Maybe he's running away with the money. - CR}{[/q2]You think the bastard just ran off with the money? - Yibis}{\q2}Será que ele não fugiu com a grana?{LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.97,0:28:21.05,Main-207+,,0,0,8,,{No way! - CR}Não, ele nunca...!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.05,0:28:24.05,Main-207+,,0,0,8,,{I don't think that he would risk\Ngetting killed trying something like that! - CR}{I'm sure he values his life! - Yibis}Ele não arriscaria a vida por uma coisa dessas.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.14,0:28:27.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I don't think so, either! - CR}Tem razão.{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.69,0:28:35.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Fala de uma vez...!{CR}{Just tell me already...! - Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.10,0:28:41.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah... P-P-Porchemy{-san}...!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.77,0:28:43.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's no use doing it anymore! - CR}{It's no use continuing! - Yibis}Não adianta!{Z/LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.78,0:28:50.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He doesn't have the energy\Nto even scream now! - CR}{He doesn't even have\Nenough energy to scream! - Yibis}Ele já nem tem energia pra gritar!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.68,0:28:57.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I bet he won't say anything and to be honest, - CR}Ele provavelmente não vai falar nada,{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.25,0:29:00.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I can't stand watching it--it's too cruel! - CR}e, pra ser sincero, é tão\Nbrutal que mal consigo assistir!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.44,0:29:03.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Show some mercy! - CR}{We should just let him go! - Yibis}Vamos soltar ele!{LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.70,0:29:09.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Look for Ace and Sabo if you\Nhave time to speak for the kid! - CR}Se tem tempo pra se preocupar com o moleque,\Nentão vai atrás do Ace e do Sabo!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.76,0:29:14.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We're the ones that are in danger\Nof death! Can't you see?! - CR}{Our lives are on the line here!\NDon't you get it?! - Yibis}É a nossa vida que tá em jogo!\NVocê não entende?!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.10,0:29:19.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We're already too late to give\Nthat money to Captain Bluejam! - CR}O prazo da entrega pro\NCapitão Bluejam já passou faz tempo!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.50,0:29:26.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{How could they do that to the little kid? - CR}Coitadinho...{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.25,0:29:28.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Should we call sheriff in the city? - CR}Devíamos chamar o xerife da cidade?{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.48,0:29:29.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's no use. - CR}{It's useless. - Yibis}Não vai adiantar.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.99,0:29:32.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{This area is not\Ncovered by the country's law. - CR}{The country's laws don't mean\Na damn thing out here. - Yibis}As leis do país não se aplicam a esta área.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.78,0:29:37.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Plus, he's a member of the Bluejam Pirates. - CR}{Besides, that guy is a member of Bluejam's crew. - Yibis}Além disso, aquele cara é da tripulação do Bluejam.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.04,0:29:39.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{And they're paying money to the Nobles. - CR}Eles pagam os nobres!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.36,0:29:44.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{They'll be overlooked for any crime and\Nmurder they commit in this country. - CR}Qualquer crime que cometam neste país\N—até assassinato—é ignorado!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.00,0:29:49.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{One more dead body will draw\Nno one's attention here. - CR}Não importa quantos cadáveres se acumulem\Npor aqui, ninguém se importa!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.00,0:29:53.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Answer me! - CR}Fala logo!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.07,0:29:55.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I won't say it. - CR}Não vou!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.31,0:30:01.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You little shit! Stop trying to\Nkeep a secret like a grown-up! - CR}{You damned brat! No secret's\Nworth this much to protect! - Yibis}Seu pirralho! Tá se esforçando demais\Npra guardar esse segredo!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.16,0:30:07.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Say it!! - CR}{Talk! - Yibis}Desembucha!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.05,0:30:11.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I won't say it! - CR}Não vou.{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.64,0:30:13.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I won't say it! - CR}Não vou!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.65,0:30:16.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I won't say it! - CR}Não vou!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.81,0:30:21.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I won't say it!! - CR}Não vou!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.12,0:30:26.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tá bom. Chega.{CR}{Fine. I've had it. - Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.72,0:30:46.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Then you die. - CR}Morre.{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.16,0:30:52.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Don't! - CR}Para!                                     Para!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.80,0:30:58.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sai da frente!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.81,0:31:04.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's him, Porchemy-san! - CR}É ele, Porchemy!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.34,0:31:06.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He stole the money from us! Damn you! - CR}{He stole our money! Damn you! - Yibis}Foi ele que roubou nossa grana, desgraçado!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.98,0:31:08.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.05,0:31:10.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A-Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.76,0:31:19.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You made it easier for us\Nby coming here voluntarily! - CR}Vocês pouparam nosso tempo vindo aqui por vontade própria!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.50,0:31:23.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tava difícil fazer\No amiguinho de vocês falar.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.51,0:31:24.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.54,0:31:26.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,M-Me solta!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.82,0:31:28.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sabo!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.20,0:31:33.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Porchemy{-san}!\N– Porchemy{-san}!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.11,0:31:38.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ace! Sabo!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.51,0:31:42.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It kind of hurts. Hey! - CR}{That kind of hurt. Hey! - Yibis}Doeu um pouquinho. Ei...!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.97,0:31:47.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Do you know what happens\Nwhen you mess with adults?! - CR}Sabe o que acontece\Nquando mexe com adultos?!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.65,0:31:50.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'll fight you! - CR}{I'll be the one to fight you! - Yibis}É comigo que você vai lutar!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.45,0:31:52.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Sabo, help him! - CR}Sabo! Pega o moleque!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.26,0:31:53.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.52,0:31:57.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele tem uma espada! Cuidado!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.04,0:32:11.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Oh, he got the knife! - CR}Ah, minha faca!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.80,0:32:13.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Porchemy{-san}, aquele moleque...!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.95,0:32:18.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vamos, Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.95,0:32:20.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Go ahead! - CR}Vai na frente!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.98,0:32:23.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You fool! Hurry up! - CR}Seu maluco! Anda logo!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.92,0:32:25.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{When I come to face someone, - CR}Quando eu encaro alguém...{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.83,0:32:28.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I won't run! - CR}eu nunca fujo!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.13,0:32:30.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que você disse?! Seu pirralho!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.74,0:32:34.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não faz isso! Ele não é como os bandidos da cidade!{CR}{Don't do it! He's not like the thugs from town! - Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.33,0:32:36.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You got that right! - CR}Seu amigo entende!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.70,0:32:39.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Alright! Enough playing around! - CR}Certo... A brincadeira acabou.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.41,0:32:44.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That's our money.\NGive it back to us peacefully, brat! - CR}{That's our money, after all.\NNow give it back without a fuss, kid! - Yibis}A grana é nossa, afinal.\NEntão devolve sem encrenca, moleque!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.55,0:32:47.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You must been possessed by\Nsome evil spirit, right? - CR}{You probably couldn't help but steal it, right? - Yibis}Provavelmente roubou por impulso, né?{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.05,0:32:50.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Give the money back so you don't regret it. - CR}Devolve a grana antes que se arrependa.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.47,0:32:55.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We have better plans for that money! - CR}A gente tem planos melhores\Npra essa grana do que vocês!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.45,0:32:57.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Wh... - CR}Quê...?{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.51,0:33:00.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What did you say?! - CR}O que você disse?!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.56,0:33:02.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Wait here for a minute! - CR}Espera aqui um minuto!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.89,0:33:06.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Stop talking crap! - CR}Chega de besteira!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.63,0:33:14.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If I'm beaten by kids, I may\Nas well quit being a pirate! - CR}Se eu perder pra dois moleques,\Né melhor eu largar a pirataria!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.94,0:33:17.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\t(2155,0,1,\c&HFEFEFE&\3c&HFEFEFE&\4c&HFEFEFE&)}{– We'll make sure you quit!\N– We'll make sure you quit! - CR}– Então pode ir largando!\N– Então pode ir largando!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.88,0:33:20.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\t(1150,0,1,\c&HFEFEFE&\3c&HFEFEFE&\4c&HFEFEFE&)}{I'm gonna kill all of you! - CR}{I'll kill you all! - Yibis}{I'll kill all three of you! - Z}Vocês tão mortos!{LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.82,0:33:32.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I heard the whole story, Porchemy. - CR}Eu soube de tudo, Porchemy...{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.33,0:33:34.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que patético.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.03,0:33:37.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Did you honestly get beaten by kids? - CR}Você perdeu mesmo pra um bando de moleques?{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.24,0:33:42.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Me desculpe, Capitão Bluejam... A grana está–
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.92,0:33:45.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Don't look at me! I don't\Neven want to see your face! - CR}Não olha pra mim! Você é uma vergonha!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.43,0:34:00.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You have a bad habit, Ace! - CR}Isso é um péssimo hábito, Ace!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.06,0:34:03.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quando você encarar um pirata de verdade, é melhor correr!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.98,0:34:06.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Por que você quer tanto morrer?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.12,0:34:10.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{This doesn't feel right. I liked the one I had. - CR}Não é a mesma coisa.\NEu gostava mais do outro.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.03,0:34:14.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We made a stupid mistake. - CR}{We made a careless mistake. - Yibis}A gente pisou feio dessa vez...{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.03,0:34:17.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The Bluejam clan won't forgive us. - CR}A tripulação do Bluejam não vai deixar isso passar.{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.90,0:34:19.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{They'll come after us! - CR}Eles vão vir atrás da gente.{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.34,0:34:23.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Oh, that was scary!\NI thought I was gonna die! - CR}Que susto!\NEu achei que ia morrer!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.14,0:34:31.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você é muito irritante! Cala a boca!\NPara de chorar!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.06,0:34:34.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I don't like cowards or people who cry a lot! - CR}{I really hate cowards and crybabies! - Yibis}Eu realmente não suporto covardes e chorões!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.63,0:34:39.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O-Obrigado!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.83,0:34:43.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.13,0:34:47.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You helped me! - CR}Vocês me salvaram!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.13,0:34:48.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você...!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.37,0:34:50.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Whoa, he's just being thankful. - CR}{Whoa, let him show gratitude. - Yibis}Ei, deixa ele agradecer.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.39,0:34:58.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Why didn't you cough it \Nup in the first place? - CR}Por que você não contou\Nlogo o que sabia?!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.40,0:35:02.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{They're the kind of people who'd kill\Nwomen or kids without hesitation! - CR}Aqueles caras matariam mulheres\Ne crianças sem hesitar!{Polly/Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.19,0:35:07.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu achei que se eu contasse...\Nvocês não iam ser meus amigos.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.49,0:35:10.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É melhor do que morrer, não é?{CR}{So what?! It's better than dying! - Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.86,0:35:13.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Why do you wanna become my friend that much? - CR}Por que você quer tanto\Nser meu amigo?!{Yibis/Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.62,0:35:17.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Porque...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.16,0:35:21.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Didn't I give you a hard time until now? - CR}{I've been giving you a hard time, remember? - Yibis}Eu não fiz a sua vida um inferno?{Z/Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.66,0:35:24.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{How could you follow me this far? - CR}Por que você me seguiu até aqui?{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.86,0:35:31.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Porque...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.21,0:35:35.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Because I have nobody else to trust! - CR}{Because I have nobody else! - Yibis}Porque eu não tenho mais ninguém!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.04,0:35:40.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I can't go back to Windmill Village\Nand I don't like the mountain bandits! - CR}Eu não posso voltar pra Vila dos Moinhos\Ne eu odeio bandidos da montanha!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.00,0:35:43.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Se eu não te seguisse, eu ia ficar sozinho!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.48,0:35:46.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ficar sozinho dói mais do que apanhar!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.46,0:35:50.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Onde estão seus pais?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.59,0:35:52.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu só tenho o meu avô.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.46,0:35:56.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Is it easy for you when I'm around? - CR}Você se sente melhor quando eu tô por perto?{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.14,0:35:56.93,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,Ahn-hã.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.94,0:36:00.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's hard without me? - CR}{You'll struggle without me? - Z}Você precisa de mim?{LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.67,0:36:00.57,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,Ahn-hã.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.52,0:36:06.26,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,"E se Gold Roger tivesse um filho?"
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.41,0:36:10.11,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{I hope that there isn't such a child! - CR}{Hopefully, such a child doesn't exist! - Yibis}Com certeza não precisamos de um moleque desses!{LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.11,0:36:15.75,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{He must be some kind of devil\Nwho'd be better off dead! - CR}{He'd be some kind of demon spawn\Nwho'd be better off dead! - Yibis}Uma cria de demônio assim nem\Nmerece estar viva!{Z/LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.28,0:36:22.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você quer que eu...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.63,0:36:24.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,viva?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.20,0:36:29.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Claro que sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.01,0:36:31.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I see. - CR}Tá...{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.72,0:36:39.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{But I don't like spoiled kids like you. - CR}{But I hate little babies like you. - Yibis}mas eu odeio pirralhos mimados como você.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.99,0:36:44.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm not spoiled! I'm strong! - CR}{I'm not a baby! I'm tough! - Yibis}Eu não sou mimado! Eu sou forte!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.12,0:36:48.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Strong?! You're not strong\Nat all! You cry like a girl! - CR}{Tough?! You're not tough at all!\NTough men don't cry! - Yibis}Forte?! Você não é nada forte!\NHomem não chora!{LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.65,0:36:53.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Have you ever gotten hit by\Na spiky thing? I'm only 7! - CR}Você já foi atingido por\Num troço cheio de espinhos? Eu só tenho sete anos!{Yibis/Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.30,0:36:58.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{When I become your age - 10, I'll\Nstop crying and become stronger! - CR}{When I'm ten like you,\NI'll stop crying and be even tougher! - Yibis}Quando eu fizer dez, igual a você,\Nvou ser super forte e nunca mais vou chorar!{LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.32,0:37:02.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I wouldn't cry even if I were\N7, stupid! I'm not like you! - CR}{I never cried when I was\Nseven, stupid! I'm not like you! - Yibis}Eu nunca chorei quando tinha sete anos,\Nseu bobo! Não me compara!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.27,0:37:05.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu vou ser mais forte do que qualquer um!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.44,0:37:09.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu prometi pro Shanks que\Neu ia me tornar um grande pirata!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.49,0:37:10.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You? Become a pirate? - CR}Pirata? Você?{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.98,0:37:11.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.61,0:37:12.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Nem pensar!\N– É sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.56,0:37:16.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tá bom, já chega!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.66,0:37:21.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, a propósito, eu tenho um probleminha.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.99,0:37:23.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê? Um problema?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.09,0:37:24.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Uh-huh. - CR}Ahn-hã...{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.09,0:37:29.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{This forest that I've been living is close\Nto where they are - the Cove of Pirates! - CR}Eu moro nessa floresta, mas é\Nperto demais daquele esconderijo na Baía dos Piratas.{Yibis/Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.73,0:37:34.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What if they attack me when\NI fall asleep exhausted? - CR}E se eles me atacarem quando eu\Nestiver exausto e dormindo?{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.91,0:37:38.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Por isso eu preciso da ajuda de vocês.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.68,0:37:58.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Why are they wounded? They're all bandaged! - CR}Como eles se machucaram?\NEstão todos enfaixados!{Yibis/Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.41,0:38:02.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, isso é...{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.63,0:38:10.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Uau! Chefe! Chefe! Temos um problema!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.20,0:38:12.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hmm? It's still early. What's wrong... - CR}{Huh? It's still early. What's wrong...? - Yibis}Hã? Ainda é cedo pra "ter problema"...{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.78,0:38:16.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Uau! O que tá acontecendo aqui?!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.75,0:38:18.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Um, dois...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.86,0:38:21.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hã?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.38,0:38:24.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ace! Luffy! Quem é esse?!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.13,0:38:27.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quem é quem?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.69,0:38:33.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{How come there is one more kid?! - CR}Por que tem mais um moleque?!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.99,0:38:35.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quem diabos é você?!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.99,0:38:37.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tá falando de mim?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.11,0:38:42.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu sou o Sabo! Ei, você deve ser a Dadan!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.43,0:38:45.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sabo? Eu já ouvi esse nome!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.71,0:38:50.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Oh yeah? That makes it easier! Thank\Nyou for taking care of me from today! - CR}Ah, é? Então facilita! Obrigado por me acolher!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.27,0:38:54.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I heard that\Nyou're a worthless brat, too! - CR}{I've heard that you're a no-good,\Ntrouble-making urchin, too! - Yibis}Eu ouvi que você é um pirralho\Ndetestável igual a eles!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.95,0:38:58.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Oh yeah? I heard that you're\Na worthless old bag, too! - CR}{Is that so? I heard that you're\Na no-good, annoying old bag! - Yibis}Ah, é? E eu ouvi que você é\Numa velha chata e imprestável!{Z/Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.08,0:39:11.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ace! Luffy! Sabo!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.39,0:39:15.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm giving you a place to stay!\NYou gotta get to work already! - CR}{I'm giving you a place to stay!\NIt's time you kids got to work! - Yibis}Eu tô dando um teto pra vocês três,\Nentão comecem a trabalhar!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.93,0:39:19.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Obrigado, Dadan!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.00,0:39:35.85,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{Ace's close friend Sabo started to live with them after being forced to leave the Gray Terminal. - CR}Depois de ser forçado a deixar o Terminal Cinza,\No melhor amigo do Ace, Sabo, se mudou pra lá.{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.24,0:39:40.08,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{Ace, Sabo, Luffy. - CR}Ace, Sabo e Luffy...{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.09,0:39:46.86,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{These three soon began spending their time fighting with wild animals in the mountain and in the jungle - CR}{The trio soon began spending their time fighting\Nthe wildlife in the mountains and the jungle. - Yibis}O trio logo começou a passar o tempo\Nlutando contra animais nas montanhas e na selva.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.88,0:39:51.40,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{and with hooligans from the\Ncity and pirates at the cove. - CR}Também se envolviam com arruaceiros\Nda cidade e piratas na baía.{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.40,0:39:58.94,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{In the end, the people at the center of the kingdom came to know their wrongdoing! - CR}{Eventually, even people living in the heart\Nof the kingdom came to know their mischief! - Yibis}Com o tempo, sua notoriedade\Nse espalhou até o coração do reino!{Z/LP}
